OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A rising number of households are      
OL,6, having their energy smart meters       
OL,7, remotely switched to prepayment meters,
OL,8, the energy regulator has said.         
OL,10,FEnergy firms can use the technology to 
OL,11,Fswap customers who are in debt to the  
OL,12,Fmore costly plan without permission.   
OL,14,FIt can leave customers, who need to top
OL,15,Fup, at risk of running out of energy.  
OL,17,FOfgem said some "vulnerable customers  
OL,18,Fhad been left without power for days or
OL,19,Feven weeks", and the energy trade body 
OL,20,Fadmitted "mistakes had been made."     
